  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More fun with friends! This game is not designed for solo play or bots.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to ruffle some feathers and plan your attack. These clucking chickens are on a mission to get their stolen eggs back, but they’ll have to dodge the furious farmer to succeed. Beware, this farmer is no chicken and he’s got plenty of tricks up his sleeve to stop you in your tracks. So sharpen your beaks, spread your wings, and get ready for the ultimate egg-venture!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/c7433fe437454ceb952d0b2b2cdbda05.webp?t=1762475937\" width=400 height=52 /></span>Alright, listen up chicken squad! You've got a farm invasion to orchestrate. Here's the plan: sneak into the farm, snatch those eggs and make a daring escape back to the coop, avoiding the farmer's traps along the way. It's time to show the farmer who's boss. Every feather counts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/c65a88129059925ce93422b8192cf388.poster.avif?t=1762475937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/c65a88129059925ce93422b8192cf388.webm?t=1762475937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/c65a88129059925ce93422b8192cf388.mp4?t=1762475937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/4e256ad7f3eff646cf55cc6ab4e3b5ab.webp?t=1762475937\" width=400 height=52 /></span>Your duty is to guard the farm, warding off those crafty chickens at all costs! Who knows what sneaky schemes they've cooked up? Lay traps, barricade your windows and guard those eggs like your life depends on it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/9266c883242e7a37069d7ee375a5882d.poster.avif?t=1762475937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/9266c883242e7a37069d7ee375a5882d.webm?t=1762475937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/9266c883242e7a37069d7ee375a5882d.mp4?t=1762475937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More fun with friends! This game is not designed for solo play or bots.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to ruffle some feathers and plan your attack. These clucking chickens are on a mission to get their stolen eggs back, but they’ll have to dodge the furious farmer to succeed. Beware, this farmer is no chicken and he’s got plenty of tricks up his sleeve to stop you in your tracks. So sharpen your beaks, spread your wings, and get ready for the ultimate egg-venture!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/c7433fe437454ceb952d0b2b2cdbda05.webp?t=1762475937\" width=400 height=52 /></span>Alright, listen up chicken squad! You've got a farm invasion to orchestrate. Here's the plan: sneak into the farm, snatch those eggs and make a daring escape back to the coop, avoiding the farmer's traps along the way. It's time to show the farmer who's boss. Every feather counts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/c65a88129059925ce93422b8192cf388.poster.avif?t=1762475937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/c65a88129059925ce93422b8192cf388.webm?t=1762475937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/c65a88129059925ce93422b8192cf388.mp4?t=1762475937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/4e256ad7f3eff646cf55cc6ab4e3b5ab.webp?t=1762475937\" width=400 height=52 /></span>Your duty is to guard the farm, warding off those crafty chickens at all costs! Who knows what sneaky schemes they've cooked up? Lay traps, barricade your windows and guard those eggs like your life depends on it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/9266c883242e7a37069d7ee375a5882d.poster.avif?t=1762475937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/9266c883242e7a37069d7ee375a5882d.webm?t=1762475937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/9266c883242e7a37069d7ee375a5882d.mp4?t=1762475937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
